name: rubystats
authors: Ilya Scharrenbroich, Bryan Donovan - http://www.bryandonovan.com, Phillip Baker
info: Ruby Stats is a port of the statistics libraries from PHPMath. Probability distributions include binomial, beta, and normal distributions with PDF, CDF and inverse CDF as well as Fisher's Exact Test.
